v>I was alone all day. Whoops</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mWa0kZx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What can I say? Woman are morbid</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VDRXzAJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They hear it if you yell loud enough</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YE1s2pg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Might as well date a lion</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/s2aR1Z2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Was she giving them away? Can I have one?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RyOWC92.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I know they were good looking for the time but it’s the aviator glasses that looks bad</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7G1FD37.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Come on!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2q5ZPBO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They never catch serial killers because they don’t think it could happen to them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LDFXNWP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I looked it up. I am traumatized.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1x9KdPy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It was his every day</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OFurSot.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My mom had to stop watching Criminal Minds so my sister and I could leave the house. She got really freaked out by the thought of what people can do.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/m14LBq2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Um, she sounds busy to me</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xaa1WXy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’m positive she enjoyed it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PFVuqPA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>TV has really educated us on how to commit the perfect crime</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bBAKorv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I can’t watch these because I have little kids so I just read about them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SJzI0D1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Did he do it?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1SSAq1j.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is why I can’t listen to cheating spouse stories either</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0TKCtBB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Maybe there’s something wrong with us or maybe we’re just trying to figure out the minds of the crazy</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nQSZxMW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>ASMR for the crime lovers</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1m1qDVn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Such a cutie</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PW3La5v.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think the hair is fine but the teeth is weird (for moms)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7d9kVLv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Don’t piss her off</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7NPeYAb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oh um, what? Tell me everything</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HhdX7d0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Wait, was she weird looking or something?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ieOZ8g3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hmm</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yEZkNYh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I guess he was okay looking</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oEf0yMS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s just like when I watch Scooby doo</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/x8BZZiT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s understandable because that became the uniform AFTER they caught several of them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vX8txwH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>All serial killers want to look like pilots?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VQzta7R.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Better than the anime p0rn coat</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/boC4tYh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nothing much, just trauma in a box</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bRk3XAq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Truly scary</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LAo9u4q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Don’t try to tempt us more</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jeTYdHG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>For reals</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/dRVrROm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GigglySprinkleCupcake]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I like this. However…</title><link>https: